"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-mayor-tom-daley-london-team-gb-paris-b2595198.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Team GB's returning Olympic stars were greeted by hoards of cheering supporters at St Pancras International as they arrived back in the UK after winning 65 medals inParis.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999996475219799, \"rank\": 3.520259432995039e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 482, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999992593714537, \"rank\": 3.8655886439160615e-07, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes travelled home by Eurostar following Sunday's closing ceremony in the French capital and were told their feats had inspired the next generation.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999964574116342, \"rank\": 3.542600919349153e-06, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}, {\"begin\": 602, \"end\": 608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8565100500154604, \"rank\": 0.11037366484295662, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among those at the station to meet them wasMayorofLondonSadiq Khan, who shook hands with the athletes on the platform and praised them for \\\"bringing the country together\\\".\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"These athletes are going to inspire another generation to get involved.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our Olympians have brought the country together and that's what's needed.\\\"\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 1007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom Daley, who revealed on his arrival in the capital that he was retiring from diving, won silver with partner Noah Williams in the synchronised 10 metre platform in Paris, his fifth Games.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.918500881360081e-43, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 1121, \"end\": 1134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}, {\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996091447, \"rank\": 3.908791178725234e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khan added: \\\"Noah Williams was inspired by Tom Daley in 2012, our canoeists say they took advantage of the facilities we built off the back of (London) 2012.\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1201, \"end\": 1205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shah_Rukh_Khan\", \"score\": 0.9999245325609087, \"rank\": 4.692002793700304e-05, \"text\": \"Khan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q33999\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shah_Rukh_Khan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shah_Rukh_Khan\"}, {\"begin\": 1214, \"end\": 1227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}, {\"begin\": 1244, \"end\": 1253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.918500881360081e-43, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 1345, \"end\": 1351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999898629994, \"rank\": 5.448982184165479e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's important to recognise that not only are the Olympics important to win the medals, but to inspire fans of a new generation.\\\"\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 65-medal haul, which included 14 golds, was the same amount won byTeam GBat the 2012 Games.\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes, many of whom wore their medals round their necks, posed for pictures with adoring fans on the platform.\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An emotional Daley, who made his Olympic debut as a 14-year-old in Beijing in 2008, said: \\\"It felt like a massive bonus because I took two years out of the sport after Tokyo and I did not know if I would get back into the team or qualify for a spot with Team GB.\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1775, \"end\": 1782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999994061, \"rank\": 5.937955409281119e-10, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1876, \"end\": 1881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9998368666456037, \"rank\": 0.00016293551980905562, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1962, \"end\": 1969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999996475219799, \"rank\": 3.520259432995039e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To come away with a medal in front of my family, it meant a lot to me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 2044, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also among the medallists was boxer Lewis Richardson, who won bronze in the 71kg category.\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2082, \"end\": 2098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_Richardson_(Hollyoaks)\", \"score\": 0.9965136461602875, \"rank\": 0.0034965034965035347, \"text\": \"Lewis Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_Richardson_(Hollyoaks)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_Richardson_(Hollyoaks)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a special Games because it was the first one in Europe since London,\\\" the 27-year-old told the PA news agency.\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2256, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2207, \"end\": 2213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999898629994, \"rank\": 5.448982184165479e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had a lot of support out here and to be honest it felt like a home games.\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been special for mine, my family's life and everyone who has been connected to my journey.\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2433, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been up there with the best times of my life.\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always felt like I can dream, but that this would only be a dream.\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To be able to turn this into a reality has been special and the highlight of my boxing career so far.\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want to celebrate this moment because there is been a lot of hard work going into this.\\\"\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson battled past Serbia's Vahid Abasov and Jordan's Zeyad Eashash before a split-decision defeat to\\u00a0Mexican Marco Verde.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2781, \"end\": 2787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.9777608797002321, \"rank\": 0.022710481203992574, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}, {\"begin\": 2807, \"end\": 2813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan\", \"score\": 0.7414702782901715, \"rank\": 0.32553486560954237, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan\"}, {\"begin\": 2864, \"end\": 2871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.6382681849032533, \"rank\": 0.5654995134381084, \"text\": \"Mexican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"I am a natural middleweight and I have dropped down to light-middleweight to make these Olympics which has been a struggle in itself, but I would not change it for the world and every struggle has been worth it.\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 3108, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The squeeze has been worth the juice because I have made memories for life.\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Light-middleweight it the most stacked division at the Games in terms of talent, the standard was extremely high.\", \"from\": 3188, \"to\": 3302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All three of my opponents were ranked above me in the world.\\\"\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3502, \"entities\": []}]}"